<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.10.2">
<l>catiriḷamaṭavār tāḻcciyaimatiyā</l>
<l>tatirkuralcaṅkat taḻakarṅ kōyiṉ</l>
<l>matitavaḻ kuṭumi māliruñ cōlai</l>
<l>patiya tētti yeḻuvatu payaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Without thinking of the lowliness of lovely young women</l>
<l>there is benefit in rising in praise of the lord</l>
<l>of Māliruñcōlai, whose summit is crawled over by the moon,</l>
<l>the temple of the beautiful one with the thunder-voiced conch.</l> 
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
